des: 107.9 Go Rock, your ultimate destination for pure, unadulterated rock in Lunenburg County! Get ready to crank up the volume and let the thunderous riffs and pounding rhythms electrify your senses. From classic anthems to the latest hits, we've got your rock cravings covered 24/7. Whether you're cruising down the highway or headbanging at home, join us on the airwaves for a non-stop adrenaline rush of guitars, drums, and unforgettable melodies.
